Package: binsegment
Type: Package
Title: Binary Segmentation Trees
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Felipe Gerard
Maintainer: Felipe Gerard <felipegerard@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides semi-automatic tools for producing client segmentations.
    It is based on the 2009 article by J. Scott Long "Group comparisons in logit and probit
using predicted probabilities".
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr
LazyData: TRUE
